{"tid":372809,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族黨:取消香港關係法請願信内容","createTime":"2017-08-24T14:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T06:50:05.000Z","uid":28366,"like":43,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"488c0e2127502ea7bd2b92f658f35e7219223eb2","tid":372809,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"敝黨於今日 (8月24日)下午發起向美國駐香港總領事館遞交公開請願信行動，就近日香港法院針對社運人士的判刑及其取消民選立法會議員資格的裁決，告知美國政府香港已喪失法治及司法獨立，要求美國政府盡快取消《美國&mdash;香港政策法1992》(即《香港關係法》）下美國對香港的所有特殊特遇。<br />\n<br />\n現公開請願信全文供各界參考。聯署安排將稍後公佈，敬請留意。<br />\n<br />\nWe organised an open letter appeal to the US Consulate today afternoon (24 August 2017).  In light of the decisions made by the Hong Kong courts to re-sentence our activists and to strip our elected legislators of their posts, we wishe to make it clear that Hong Kong&rsquo;s Rule of Law and judicial independence are both, in all meanings relevant, dead.  Our open letter appeals to the US to abolish all special distinctions it deems between Hong Kong and China, as stated in the United States-Hong Kong Policy Act.<br />\n<br />\nFull content of the appeal letter is now available. Arrangement for the public to join the appeal will be announced in due course.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nhcbfpg1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnhcbfpg1&h=4395a16c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pmqb8t1h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpmqb8t1h&h=322745ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x3pr4yus\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx3pr4yus&h=15ac60c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qxjf4a37\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqxjf4a37&h=e5e4b75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2oswrl0q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2os